      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for optimized valve timing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically sound, with documented rod bearing service and proactive rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and factory dampening. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains exceptionally strong, pulling cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with the characteristic metallic rasp of a healthy S54.",
